data.description:
Welcome to this exquisite residence nestled in the sought-after Countryside neighborhood where the brand new windows add a touch of elegance. As you step inside, your senses will be captivated by the soaring ceilings, a charming custom wood plank wall, and an inviting bay window that bathes the space in natural light. 

The upper level of this home boasts three spacious bedrooms, a well-appointed main bathroom, and the convenience of a laundry area. On the main level, you'll discover a cozy family room, a modern kitchen, and a welcoming dining area - perfect for entertaining and everyday living. 

Descend to the lower level, where you'll find a comfortable living room that opens up to your backyard, complete with a lovely patio, creating an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. 

This home enjoys a prime, central location with easy access to Boulder, the North Metro area, and major transportation routes. Plus, you'll appreciate the proximity to the Westminster dog park and the scenic Stanley Lake, both just a leisurely stroll away. 
 
Don't miss the opportunity to envision yourself living in this splendid home – schedule your visit today!
